UTM and Gamuda Land Establish Strategic Partnership with MoU Signing Ceremony on World Wetlands Day
===================================================================================================

by [norainismail](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/author/norainismail/ "Posts by norainismail")
 | Feb 27, 2024 | [News](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/category/news/)
, [Uncategorized](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/category/uncategorized/)

![](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/4-980x663.png)

**SELANGOR, 3 Feb.** – Universiti Teknologi Malaysia (UTM) and Gamuda Land Sdn. Bhd. (GAMUDA) signed a  Memorandum of Understanding (MoU) at the Wetlands Arboretum Centre at Gamuda Cove, Kuala Langat, Selangor here today.  [https://news.utm.my/ms/2024/02/utm-and-gamuda-land-establish-strategic-partnership-with-mou-signing-ceremony-on-world-wetlands-day/](https://news.utm.my/ms/2024/02/utm-and-gamuda-land-establish-strategic-partnership-with-mou-signing-ceremony-on-world-wetlands-day/)
